{"tid":975340,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"餐飯食到一半先發現原來自己食緊人哋食剩嘅嘢...","createTime":"2019-01-09T14:12:41.000Z","updateTime":"2019-01-09T19:31:03.000Z","uid":190211,"like":38,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"ed0de502642921cad8cf2476c296f36effc44e86","tid":975340,"uid":190211,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-09T14:12:41.000Z","msg":"話說啱啱去咗中環一間野叫吱_朕 我同友人嗌咗一碟燒鯖魚 過咗陣個waiter送咗依條野黎 一開始我仲心諗點解咁岩岩蠶蠶 冇咗頭同尾 好似俾人食過咁 仲心諗點解咁凍 不過我冇為意同埋又費事講 個fd仲話好好食 keep住係咁食 我地以為佢啲份量係咁細 之後過咗差唔多成半個鐘 佢又上咗一條新嘅燒鯖魚 重點係條魚完整無缺 仲要冒煙 之後我同佢講話啱啱上過嚟 佢好疑惑咁望住我 我就知今鋪賴嘢.... <img src=\"https://na.cx/i/FKJ7OM3.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FFKJ7OM3.png&h=5b37c364&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"16dc2b3dbfd1caf05ee20028710883959cb4087f","tid":975340,"uid":26540,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-09T14:13:40.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bang.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6697b6e192153d871c508be0e318d696bae65cb4","tid":975340,"uid":228266,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-09T14:14:50.000Z","msg":"呢啲一定要投訴..."},{"pid":"8b55616f3724bc794fa350f88d4db86c2894089a","tid":975340,"uid":190211,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"6697b6e192153d871c508be0e318d696bae65cb4","tid":975340,"uid":228266,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-09T14:14:50.000Z","msg":"呢啲一定要投訴..."},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-09T14:15:37.000Z","msg":"但係我哋食晒成碟野先發現喎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f1594d03beddcd3ee2a50796e7c0baee32e148d3","tid":975340,"uid":15193,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-09T14:16:49.000Z","msg":"看圖說故事<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bang.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b053c08fbb9c38b0c590185b0530cf7cc83dbeb5","tid":975340,"uid":142532,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-0